|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"伸缩组支持关联负载均衡实例，通过负载均衡实例将访问流量分发到伸缩组内的多个实例中，可以有效增强伸缩组的服务能力，您可以调用API AttachLoadBalancers添加一个或多个负载均衡实例。","title":"添加一个或多个负载均衡实例"},{"id":160523682,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyScheduledTask","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScheduledTaskId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"如果当前伸缩组的定时任务不能满足业务需求，您可以调用ModifyScheduledTask接口，通过指定定时任务的ID修改已有定时任务的配置参数：需要执行的伸缩规则、伸缩组内实例数量、任务执行频率、重试策略等。","title":"修改一个定时任务的信息"},{"id":160523683,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeRegions","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"在使用弹性伸缩前，您可以先通过调用API DescribeRegions查询可以在哪些地域使用弹性伸缩服务，方便您选择最适合的地域和可用区来使用弹性伸缩服务，确保在所选地域内获得良好的访问性能。","title":"查询可以使用弹性伸缩服务的地域"},{"id":160523684,"product":"Ess","name":"RecordLifecycleActionHeartbeat","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"如果伸缩组内生命周期挂钩触发后被挂起的ECS实例的等待时间不能满足您的自定义操作，在ECS实例被挂起状态下，调用RecordLifecycleActionHeartbeat，通过指定生命周期挂钩的ID、伸缩活动的等待状态标识符、需设置的等待时间等配置参数，延长挂起时间。","title":"延长生命周期挂钩触发后ECS实例被挂起等待时间"},{"id":160523685,"product":"Ess","name":"ScaleWithAdjustment","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-03-13T11:03:01.000Z","summary":"区别于ExecuteScalingRule接口，您无需提前创建伸缩规则，直接调用API ScaleWithAdjustment接口快速基于指定调整规则触发弹性扩缩容。","title":"基于指定调整规则触发性扩缩容"},{"id":160523686,"product":"Ess","name":"ListTagValues","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"调用API ListTagValues查询弹性伸缩资源标签键对应的标签值，能够帮助您更好地了解弹性伸缩资源，实现资源的有效分类和管理。","title":"查询弹性伸缩资源标签键对应的标签值"},{"id":160523687,"product":"Ess","name":"CreateNotificationConfiguration","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:28.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:33.000Z","summary":"调用API CreateNotificationConfiguration创建弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知，帮助您及时掌握伸缩组的动态，进一步实现弹性伸缩事件的自动化管理。","title":"创建弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知"},{"id":160523688,"product":"Ess","name":"CreateScalingConfiguration","version":"2