n删除该条弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知。","title":"删除一条弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知"},{"id":160523707,"product":"Ess","name":"SetGroupDeletionProtection","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"如果开启伸缩组删除保护功能后，此时不能删除该伸缩组；如果关闭伸缩组删除保护功能，此时可直接删除该伸缩组，本文为您介绍如何调用API SetGroupDeletionProtection为伸缩组开启或关闭伸缩组删除保护功能。","title":"为伸缩组开启或关闭删除保护"},{"id":160523708,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyAlarm","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"AlarmTaskId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"修改一个报警任务。","title":"修改报警任务"},{"id":160523709,"product":"Ess","name":"DeleteAlarm","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"AlarmTaskId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"针对具有突发性或时间上不易预测的业务，您可以通过报警任务关联云监控指标进行管理。弹性伸缩会实时统计指标数据，在统计值满足报警条件时触发报警，并在生效周期内自动执行伸缩规则，动态调整伸缩组内的ECS实例或ECI实例数量。如果您不再使用当前的报警任务，您也可以调用API DeleteAlarm直接删除该报警任务。","title":"删除一个报警任务"},{"id":160523710,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeScalingInstances","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"调用DescribeScalingInstances，通过伸缩组ID查询该伸缩组内的ECS实例列表及实例信息，包括当前伸缩组中，运行状态的抢占式实例总数、ECS实例总数、ECS实例的预热状态、生命周期状态等。同时也支持指定实例健康状态、生命周期状态、创建方式等筛选符合要求的ECS实例。","title":"查询伸缩组内ECS实例列表"},{"id":160523711,"product":"Ess","name":"DeleteLifecycleHook","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"LifecycleHookId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"如果您不再需要一个生命周期挂钩，可以调用API DeleteLifecycleHook删除该生命周期挂钩，以空出挂钩配额。","title":"删除一个生命周期挂钩"},{"id":160523712,"product":"Ess","name":"ExecuteScalingRule","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"执行伸缩规则可以实现手动或自动调整ECS实例或ECI实例资源。其中，对于简单规则和步进规则，您才可以调用API ExecuteScalingRule执行一条伸缩规则，而对于目标追踪规则和预测规则，弹性伸缩会自动执行伸缩规则。","title":"执行一条伸缩规则"},{"id":160523714,"product":"Ess","name":"DetachAlbServerGroups","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"调用DetachAlbServerGroups，并可以指定伸缩组的ID、ALB 服务器组的ID、ALB 服务器组中 ECS 实例使用的端口号等参数，实现从伸缩组中移出一个或多个ALB服务器组。","title":"移出一个或多个ALB服务器组"},{"id":160523715,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeScheduledTasks","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScheduledTaskIds\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-07-04T02:10:59.000Z","summary":"定时任务是一种预设任务，可以在指定时间执行指定的伸缩规则，实现计算资源的自动扩缩容。定时任务创建完成后，您可以调用API DescribeScheduledTasks查询定时任务的详细信息，例如，定时任务的触发时间点、定时任务总数、执行定时任务的伸缩组的ID等。","title":"查询定时任务的信息"},{"id":160523716,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyEciScalingConfiguration","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingConfigurationId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-06-24T18:01:23.000Z","summary":"调用ModifyEciScalingConfiguration，并可以指定待修改伸缩配置的ID、伸缩配置的名称、ECI实例的属性等参数，修改伸缩配置，例如实例重启策略、实例的抢占策略、弹性公网 IP 的带宽等信息。","title":"修改一个ECI类型伸缩配置"},{"id":160523717,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeNotificationTypes","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"调用DescribeNotificationTypes接口，查询弹性伸缩组的弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知的类型，例如：扩容伸缩活动成功，缩容伸缩活动成功，定时任务到期提醒，弹性扩容活动部分成功等。","title":"查询弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知的类型"},{"id":160523718,"product":"Ess","name":"AttachAlbServerGroups","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"对于需要动态调整实例数量来应对业务变化负载以及确保应用程序的高可用性场景，调用API AttachAlbServerGroups向伸缩组添加一个或多个ALB服务器组，可以在业务变化时自动实现弹性扩展，并根据负载情况动态分配流量、提高应用程序的稳定性。","title":"添加一个或多个ALB服务器组"},{"id":160523719,"product":"Ess","name":"CreateScalingRule","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:33.000Z","summary":"伸缩规则的作用由伸缩规则的类型来决定，可用于触发伸缩活动或者智能设置伸缩组边界值。根据不同业务需求，通过调用API CreateScalingRule创建不同类型的伸缩规则，例如，业务需要只能设置伸缩组边界值，建议您选择预测规则类型。","title":"创建一条伸缩规则"},{"id":160523720,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyNotificationConfiguration","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\",\"NotificationArn\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"事件通知支持在发生指定类型的事件后，自动发送消息到云监控、MNS主题和MNS队列，可以帮助您及时掌握伸缩组的动态，进一步实现自动化管理。如果当前事件通知的类型不再满足业务需求，您可以调用API ModifyNotificationConfiguration修改弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知，您无需重新创建新的事件通知，但不支持修改事件通知的通知方式。","title":"修改一条弹性伸缩事件及资源变化通知"},{"id":160523721,"product":"Ess","name":"RemoveInstances","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-21T09:41:54.000Z","summary":"如果当前伸缩组状态为启用状态，且伸缩组内不存在执行中的伸缩活动，您可以调用API RemoveInstances从一个伸缩组删除一台或多台不再需要的实例。","title":"从一个伸缩组删除一台或多台实例"},{"id":160523722,"product":"Ess","name":"AttachVServerGroups","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"伸缩组关联负载均衡实例（CLB）后，加入伸缩组的实例会自动添加为CLB实例的后端服务器，处理来自CLB实例转发的访问请求。当需要将不同的请求转发到不同的后端服务器上时，或需要通过域名和URL进行请求转发时，您可以调用API AttachVServerGroups来添加负载均衡实例下的一个或者多个虚拟服务器组，通过虚拟服务器组管理不同的后端服务器。","title":"添加负载均衡实例下虚拟服务器组"},{"id":160523723,"product":"Ess","name":"CreateScheduledTask","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:33.000Z","summary":"定时任务是一种预设任务，您可以通过调用API CreateScheduledTask创建一个定时任务，在指定时间执行指定伸缩规则，实现计算资源的自动扩张或收缩，来满足业务需求的同时又能控制成本。","title":"创建一个定时任务"},{"id":160523724,"product":"Ess","name":"DeleteScheduledTask","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScheduledTaskId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"针对业务量的变化时间可预测的场景，您可以通过配置定时任务，在业务高峰到达前已准备好充足的计算资源，或者在业务高峰后及时释放空闲的计算资源，满足业务需求的同时又能控制成本。如果当前定时任务不再使用，您也可以调用API DeleteScheduledTask直接删除该定时任务。","title":"删除一个定时任务"},{"id":160523725,"product":"Ess","name":"RebalanceInstances","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-06T07:46:34.000Z","summary":"如果由于库存不足等原因导致可用区之间ECS实例的数量不均衡，您可以通过调用API RebalanceInstances重新平衡多可用区伸缩组内ECS实例的分布。","title":"重新平衡ECS实例分布"},{"id":160523726,"product":"Ess","name":"VerifyAuthentication","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-12-21T06:05:38.000Z","summary":"调用VerifyAuthentication并指定主账号的ID，检测账号是否已有服务关联角色AliyunServiceRoleForAutoScaling，用于授权弹性伸缩操作ECS和ECI资源。","title":"检测是否已授权弹性伸缩操作ECS和ECI资源"},{"id":160523727,"product":"Ess","name":"DetachVServerGroups","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"伸缩组支持关联负载均衡实例，可以有效增强伸缩组的服务能力。如果您的业务暂不需要通过负载均衡实例将访问流量分发到伸缩组内的多个实例中去，您可以调用API DetachVServerGroups移除一个或者多个虚拟服务器组。","title":"移除一个或者多个虚拟服务器组"},{"id":160523728,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyScalingGroup","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"如果您需要根据业务变动需求与策略自动增加或减少指定类型的实例数量，则可以通过配置伸缩组来自动调整您的业务计算能力（即实例数量）。如果当前伸缩组属性不再满足业务需求，则您可以调用API ModifyScalingGroup修改伸缩组属性（例如最大实例数、最小实例数或期望实例数等属性），避免重新创建伸缩组并重新配置相关属性，节省了时间和资源成本。","title":"修改一个伸缩组"},{"id":160523729,"product":"Ess","name":"ListTagResources","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ResourceIds\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"调用API ListTagResources查询一个或多个弹性伸缩资源已经绑定的标签列表，可以帮助您更好地分类和管理弹性伸缩资源的使用情况，实现资源的自动化管理和权限控制等目标。","title":"查询弹性伸缩资源已经绑定的标签列表"},{"id":160523730,"product":"Ess","name":"UntagResources","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ResourceIds\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2022-09-09T07:26:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"调用API UntagResources为指定的弹性伸缩资源列表统一解绑标签，可以简化资源管理、提高系统性能优化、降低安全风险。解绑标签后，如果该标签没有绑定其他任何资源，则会被自动删除。","title":"为指定的弹性伸缩资源列表统一解绑标签"},{"id":160523731,"product":"Ess","name":"EnterStandby","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[