erGroups从伸缩组移除一个或多个负载均衡服务器组，支持的服务器组类型包括应用型负载均衡ALB和网络型负载均衡NLB，可以实现对负载均衡策略的动态调整，并帮助提高系统的高可用性。","title":"移除一个或多个负载均衡服务器组"},{"id":238388503,"product":"Ess","name":"AttachServerGroups","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":"[\"ScalingGroupId\"]","body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2023-02-06T02:17:35.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-05-22T06:39:18.000Z","summary":"对于需要动态调整实例数量来应对业务变化负载以及确保应用程序的高可用性场景，调用API AttachServerGroups为伸缩组添加一个或多个负载均衡服务器组，支持的服务器组类型包括应用型负载均衡ALB和网络型负载均衡NLB，可以在业务变化时自动实现弹性扩展，并根据负载情况动态分配流量、提高应用程序的稳定性。","title":"添加一个或多个负载均衡服务器组"},{"id":340721775,"product":"Ess","name":"ApplyScalingGroup","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST","protocol":"HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":15000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2024-01-04T08:12:29.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-07-03T10:46:09.000Z","summary":"如果您需要通过配置文件方式快速创建、管理伸缩组，则可以通过调用API ApplyScalingGroup来创建和管理伸缩组。","title":"基于配置文件管理伸缩组"},{"id":341715834,"product":"Ess","name":"ModifyInstanceAttribute","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2024-01-11T06:40:34.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-06-24T18:01:23.000Z","summary":"调用ModifyInstanceAttribute，并指定伸缩组内实例的ID、伸缩组的ID、伸缩组所属的地域ID等参数，修改伸缩组中一台ECS实例的部分信息，目前仅支持修改手动添加到伸缩组中实例的生命周期托管属性。","title":"修改伸缩组内实例的部分信息"},{"id":347894648,"product":"Ess","name":"ApplyEciScalingConfiguration","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST","protocol":"HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":15000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2024-02-21T07:07:35.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-02-28T02:49:26.000Z","summary":"如果您需要通过配置文件方式快速创建和管理ECI类型的伸缩配置，则可以通过调用API ApplyEciScalingConfiguration来创建或更新ECI类型的伸缩配置。","title":"基于配置文件管理伸缩配置"},{"id":347894649,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeScalingGroupDetail","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2024-02-21T07:07:35.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-02-28T02:49:34.000Z","summary":"您可以通过调用API DescribeScalingGroupDetail查询该伸缩组详情，例如，查看指定伸缩组的基本信息、伸缩组内实例、伸缩配置等信息。当ECI类型的伸缩组指定OutputFormat参数为YAML时，可以输出Kubernetes Deployment YAML格式内容。","title":"查询指定伸缩组详情"},{"id":347894650,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribeEciScalingConfigurationDetail","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"POST|GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_props":"","createdAt":"2024-02-21T07:07:35.000Z","updatedAt":"2024-02-28T02:24:47.000Z","summary":"调用API DescribeEciScalingConfigurationDetail，通过伸缩组的伸缩配置ID查询对应的伸缩配置信息（例如临时存储空间大小、IPv6地址数、弹性公网IP的带宽等），支持输出为YAML格式。","title":"查询ECI类型伸缩配置信息"},{"id":360209022,"product":"Ess","name":"DescribePatternTypes","version":"2022-02-22","parameter_type":"Single","method":"GET","protocol":"HTTP|HTTPS","path":"/","business":null,"response_headers":"[]","timeout":10000,"deprecated":0,"hidden":0,"resource_type_code":null,"resource_type_title":null,"resource_params":null,"body_style":null,"site_p